Termubit Specification: 0071
 Title: Payment Protocol MIME Types for Termubit
 Author: Aldianokto <aldianokto@proton.me>
 Status: Draft
 Type: Standards Track
 Created: 2026-06-18

== Abstract ==
This document defines the MIME (RFC 2046) Media Type for Termubit payment protocol message files.

== Specification ==
The MIME types used for Termubit payment protocol messages are:

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Message !! Type/Subtype
|-
| PaymentRequest || application/vnd.termubit.payment.request
|-
| Payment || application/vnd.termubit.payment.payment
|-
| PaymentACK || application/vnd.termubit.payment.ack
|}

